<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Home | Elderly Assistance</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #f4f9ff;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #74ebd5, #acb6e5);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;  /* Slightly smaller text */
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .btn-custom {
            min-width: 140px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .alert {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .role-label {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        dotlottie-wc {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero shadow-sm d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center flex-column">
            <script src="https://unpkg.com/@lottiefiles/dotlottie-wc@0.6.2/dist/dotlottie-wc.js" type="module"></script>
            <dotlottie-wc src="https://lottie.host/d5c8731c-1d46-4d99-a28e-3a19f8618551/k9PZJ8Za2u.lottie" speed="1" autoplay loop></dotlottie-wc>
            <h1>Welcome to Elderly Assistance</h1>
            <p>Connecting elderly individuals with kind-hearted volunteers for daily support</p>

            <% if (messages && messages.length > 0) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-success text-start mt-4">
                    <% messages.forEach(function(message) { %>
                        <p class="mb-0"><%= message %></p>
                    <% }); %>
                </div>

                <p class="mt-4">
                    Hello, <strong><%= user.first_name %> <%= user.last_name %></strong>
                    <span class="role-label">
                        <% if (user.role === 'elderly') { %> (üëµ Elderly)
                        <% } else { %> (ü§ù Volunteer)
                        <% } %>
                    </span>
                </p>

                <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-light btn-custom mt-3">Logout</a>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 mt-4">
                    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-light btn-custom">Register</a>
                    <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-custom">Login</a>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row text-center">
            <h2 class="mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="lead">
                We aim to bridge the gap between elderly individuals in need and compassionate volunteers,
                ensuring no one is ever left without support in their daily lives.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="row text-center mt-5">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">üßì For the Elderly</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Easily request help for errands, medication, or companionship.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">ü§ù For Volunteers</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Browse and fulfill help requests with filters and tracking tools.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">üîê Secure & Simple</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Role-based access with a clean, friendly interface for all users.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container text-center mt-5 mb-5">
            <p class="mt-3 text-muted">Together, we make life easier ‚Äî one act of kindness at a time.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
